Dan Bulan mati</i>

293
00:28:27,125 --> 00:28:30,083
<i>Dalam angin hitam
Bintang-bintang akan mati</i>

294
00:28:35,541 --> 00:28:37,125
Bersiaplah.

295
00:28:43,583 --> 00:28:44,666
Apa itu?

296
00:28:45,458 --> 00:28:46,708
Mayat hidup.

297
